<p style="text-align: justify;"></p>";s:10:"post_title";s:124:"Selena Gomez, Maisie Williams, Rita Ora, Irina Shayk, Hailey Baldwin Show off Their Delicate Side at The Fashion Awards 2017";s:12:"post_excerpt";s:0:"";s:11:"post_status";s:7:"publish";s:14:"comment_status";s:4:"open";s:11:"ping_status";s:4:"open";s:13:"post_password";s:0:"";s:9:"post_name";s:107:"selena-gomez-maisie-williams-rita-ora-irina-shayk-hailey-baldwin-show-off-delicate-side-fashion-awards-2017";s:7:"to_ping";s:0:"";s:6:"pinged";s:0:"";s:13:"post_modified";s:19:"2017-12-05 14:56:55";s:17:"post_modified_gmt";s:19:"2017-12-05 14:56:55";s:21:"post_content_filtered";s:0:"";s:11:"post_parent";s:1:"0";s:4:"guid";s:27:"http://wikiceleb.com/?p=211";s:10:"menu_order";s:1:"0";s:9:"post_type";s:4:"post";s:14:"post_mime_type";s:0:"";s:13:"comment_count";s:1:"0";}i:6;O:8:"stdClass":23:{s:2:"ID";s:3:"242";s:11:"post_author";s:1:"1";s:9:"post_date";s:19:"2017-12-08 14:21:42";s:13:"post_date_gmt";s:19:"2017-12-08 14:21:42";s:12:"post_content";s:7644:"&nbsp;
<p style="text-align: justify;">Whenever anyone talks about one of the most influential method actors of Hollywood, they cannot miss one name and that is Christian Charles Philip Bale. The Oscar-winning star was born on 30 January 1974 as the son of Jenny, an English circus performer and David Bale, a South African commercial pilot. His family lived in many countries throughout Bale‚Äôs childhood such as England, Portugal and the United States. He has often acknowledged that the frequent relocations have drawn him towards his career choice. He attended Bournemouth school until age 16.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong>His journey in the industry</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Christian was 8 when he acted in a commercial for a fabric softener <strong>Lenor.</strong> After his parents got divorced he shifted to Los Angeles with his father.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong><em>The 90‚Äôs</em></strong></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-245" src="http://wikiceleb.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/preview_christian-charles-philip-bale-300x169.jpeg" alt="" width="656" height="369" /></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Bale debuted in the film industry as <em>Tsarevich Alexei Nikolaevich</em> in <strong>Anasthesia: The Mystery of Anna</strong> (1986). Then he acted in many lead roles in movies like <strong>Heart of the country</strong>, <strong>Mio in the Land of Faraway</strong>, <strong>Empire of The Sun</strong> (1987) for which he was immensely praised. After that he acted in <strong>Henry V</strong>(1989) and <strong>Treasure Island</strong> (1990). Moreover he was seen in musical films <strong>Newsies</strong> and <strong>Swing Kids.</strong></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><strong><em>The 2000s</em></strong></p>
<img class="aligncenter wp-image-246" src="http://wikiceleb.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/2000s-300x225.jpg" alt="" width="576" height="432" />

&nbsp;
<p style="text-align: justify;">In 2000 one of the most controversial movies of Bale <strong>American Psycho</strong> was released, he spent months to achieve ‚ÄòOlympian figure‚Äô as needed for his role. Bale‚Äôs performance in the movie was termed as heroic. Additionally, in 2002, he was starred in three main features films named <strong>Laurel Canyon</strong>, <strong>Reign of</strong> <strong>Fire</strong> and <strong>Equilibrium</strong>. Then he played <em>Trevor Reznik</em> in 2004 psychological thriller <strong>The Machinist</strong>, his acting and devotion to the role was widely praised as he dropped to 100lb. to play a severe insomniac. After his success in The Machinist, Bale bagged the role of Batman in Christopher Nolan‚Äôs <strong>Batman trilogy</strong>. For the role he had to be 190 lb. in six months, the whole experience was tough for him but Bale‚Äôs hard work and dedication didn‚Äôt stop him from gaining the required weight for Batman in the asserted time. Consequently <strong>Batman</strong> <strong>Begins</strong> released in 2005, the movie was an international triumph and Bale‚Äôs role was praised by critics and fans as well.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Furthermore, Christian acted on several films like <strong>Harsh times</strong> (2006), <strong>Rescue Dawn</strong> (2006), <strong>The Prestige</strong> (2006), and <strong>I</strong> <strong>am Not There</strong> (2007). The highly anticipated <strong>The Dark Knight</strong> was released in 2008 and was widely praised as expected. Subsequently, he starred in <strong>Terminator Salvation</strong> (2009) and <strong>Public Enemies</strong> (2009). Thereby, in 2011 <strong>The Fighter</strong> was released where he played the role of <em>Dicky Eklund </em>for which he lost 14 kg (30lb), the film and his performance were universally acclaimed.</p>
<script async src="//pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js"></script>
<ins class="adsbygoogle"
