REAL MADRID VS SEVILLA FC
<p style="text-align: justify;">The game on 9<sup>th</sup> December 2017 at Santiago Bernabeu for the 15<sup>th</sup> round league game on LA LIGA showed that Real Madrid was back in their form after two draws against Athletic and Fuenlabrada in LA LIGA and COPA DEL REY. With the key players missing the young squad performed very well. Real Madrid was able to score five goals in the first half and the game ended with a final score of 5-0.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">At the beginning of game Nacho managed to score a goal. The brilliant shot from Lucas Vazquez was denied by Sergio Rico that turned into a corner where Nacho was able to score.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-280" src="http://wikiceleb.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/3-1-300x161.png" alt="" width="462" height="248" /></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">At 23<sup>rd</sup> minute of the game, C.Ronaldo was able to score with the assist from Marco Asensio. The real striker finishes to the bottom left of the goal post. The attacking play from Real Madrid dominated Sevilla.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-281" src="http://wikiceleb.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/1-3-300x232.jpg" alt="" width="466" height="360" /></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">At 31<sup>st</sup> minute J.Navas was given a yellow card for his handball inside D Box that turned into penalty and C.Ronaldo was again able to score from the spot.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-282" src="http://wikiceleb.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/2-3-300x200.jpg" alt="" width="477" height="318" /></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">With the attacking mode on Real Madrid, they were able to score a goal on a counter, Toni Kroos marked himself into the score sheet assisted by Lucas Vazquez. Similarly, Karim Benzema assisted Achraf for another goal at 42<sup>nd</sup> minute of the game.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><img class="aligncenter wp-image-283" src="http://wikiceleb.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/4-300x158.png" alt="" width="503" height="265" /></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">In the first half of the game real Madrid was able to score five goals dominating and extending their superiority. Sevilla with 5<sup>th</sup> position in LA LIGA league table was not able to perform that well in this particular match. Captain from Sevilla wants to apologize to their fans for not performing well and has promised not to repeat the similar mistakes in upcoming games.</p>
<p style="text-align: justify;">At the end of the day, the Real Madrid was able to grab 3 points even without the presence of some of the key players like S.Ramos, Carvajal, Casemiro¬†and G.Bale.</p>
