<p style="text-align: justify;"></p>";s:10:"post_title";s:76:"Real Madrid Back To Their Regular Best (‚ÄúReal Madrid VS Sevilla Fc 5-0‚Äù)";s:12:"post_excerpt";s:0:"";s:11:"post_status";s:7:"publish";s:14:"comment_status";s:4:"open";s:11:"ping_status";s:4:"open";s:13:"post_password";s:0:"";s:9:"post_name";s:59:"real-madrid-back-regular-best-real-madrid-vs-sevilla-fc-5-0";s:7:"to_ping";s:0:"";s:6:"pinged";s:0:"";s:13:"post_modified";s:19:"2017-12-09 18:19:42";s:17:"post_modified_gmt";s:19:"2017-12-09 18:19:42";s:21:"post_content_filtered";s:0:"";s:11:"post_parent";s:1:"0";s:4:"guid";s:27:"http://wikiceleb.com/?p=279";s:10:"menu_order";s:1:"0";s:9:"post_type";s:4:"post";s:14:"post_mime_type";s:0:"";s:13:"comment_count";s:1:"0";}i:8;O:8:"stdClass":23:{s:2:"ID";s:3:"302";s:11:"post_author";s:1:"1";s:9:"post_date";s:19:"2017-12-11 17:08:08";s:13:"post_date_gmt";s:19:"2017-12-11 17:08:08";s:12:"post_content";s:9967:"<p style="text-align: justify;">Actor and actress are revered as heroes to many across the world and there‚Äôs no surprise that with such fame and adoration comes staggering wealth. It‚Äôs easy to assume that the beautiful celebrities we see on our big and small screens are rich beyond their wildest dreams. But have you ever taken a moment to consider who the real wealthiest movie star?
We are here to reveal the list.</p>

<ol style="text-align: justify;" start="9">
 	<li><strong>SYLVESTER STALLONE</strong>
Net Worth: $400 Million</li>
</ol>
<p style="text-align: justify;">Sylvester Stallone is an American actor and filmmaker, born on July 6, 1946.He is famous for the title character of <strong>Rocky series </strong>and John Rambo from movie <strong>Rambo</strong>. As a young aspiring actor in 1970s, Sylvester became so poor that he even had to sell his beloved dog but there is a happy end to this tale as once his journey to superstardom began he bought his dog back for the much higher price. He then seen in a Rambo film along with other high profile roles, Stallone managed to earn 400 million dollars.</p>
<img class="aligncenter wp-image-294" src="http://wikiceleb.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/1-4-300x150.jpg" alt="" width="430" height="215" />

<img class="aligncenter wp-image-295" src="http://wikiceleb.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/2-4-300x150.jpg" alt="" width="427" height="214" />
<ol style="text-align: justify;" start="8">
 	<li><strong>¬†JOHNNY DEPP</strong>
Net Worth: $400 Million</li>
</ol>
<p style="text-align: justify;">He is one of the biggest male lead over the last 25 years who managed to earn so much money, thanks to performances and savvy business deals related to the <a href="http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0325980/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><strong>Pirates of the Caribbean</strong></a> franchise as well as high profile collaborations. He takes more than 20 million dollars per film, the highest figure of any actor in Hollywood. In 2012, he was even listed in the Guinness World Book of Records as being the highest-paid actor with annual earnings of a whopping 75 dollars. But currently, he is facing some financial problems. He spends 2 million dollars per month for his lifestyle and 30 thousand dollars on wine per month.</p>
<img class="aligncenter wp-image-296" src="http://wikiceleb.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/3-3-300x188.jpg" alt="" width="438" height="274" />

<img class="aligncenter wp-image-297" src="http://wikiceleb.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/4-3-300x169.jpg" alt="" width="437" height="246" />
<ol style="text-align: justify;" start="7">
 	<li><strong>AMITABH BACHCHAN</strong>
Net Worth: $425 Million</li>
</ol>
<p style="text-align: justify;">He is the most iconic name in the Indian Film Industry .he started his career in the 1970s and famously known as the angry man in his more than 40 years career and comprising of 180 plus films most of which were blockbusters. Movie lovers might recognize him from his 2013 Hollywood debut role in The Great Gatsby along with Leonardo DiCaprio.</p>
<img class="aligncenter wp-image-298" src="http://wikiceleb.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/5-2-300x169.jpg" alt="" width="432" height="244" />

<img class="aligncenter wp-image-299" src="http://wikiceleb.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/12/6-2-300x200.jpg" alt="" width="420" height="281" />
<ol style="text-align: justify;" start="6">
 	<li><strong>MEL GIBSON
</strong> Net worth: $426 Million</li>
</ol>
