<p style="text-align: justify;">There is no denying that Tom Cruise is one of the first names on anyone‚Äôs list when it comes to huge Hollywood name stars and he certainly has the wealth to support that claim in a long and fruitful career that has seen him become both a bonafide action star and dramatic performer. Cruz has made hit after hit from Top Gun <strong>to Mission Impossible</strong> to <strong>Jack Reacher</strong>. Of course, when your level of celebrity reaches as Tom Cruiser‚Äôs the salaries you can command get bigger and bigger. Some of Cruz‚Äôs biggest paydays have been 25 million dollars for 2015‚Äôs <strong>Mission Impossible: Rogue Nation</strong>, 20 million dollars for 2008‚Äôs <strong>Valkyrie </strong>and 25 million dollars for 2003‚Äôs <strong>The Last Samurai</strong> and staggering total check for 75 million dollars each for <strong>Mission Impossible 2 &amp; 3.</strong></p>
